interface PackageProps {

// id: string;

title: string;

shortDesc: string;

durationDays: number;

imageCover: string;

}

export default function PackageList({

// id,

title,

shortDesc,

durationDays,

imageCover,

}: PackageProps) {

return (

<>

<img

src={imageCover}

className="w-full h-48 object-cover rounded-lg"

alt={title}

/>

<div className="mt-3">

<h2 className="text-lg font-semibold">{title}</h2>

<p className="text-yellow-500 text-sm">⭐ {durationDays} / 5</p>

<p className="text-gray-700 text-sm mt-2 line-clamp-2">{shortDesc}</p>

</div>

</>

);

}

import { getAllPackages } from "../api/Packages.api";

export const useAllPackages = () => {

return useQuery({

queryKey: ["packages"],

queryFn: getAllPackages,

});

};
